==============================================
Readme for the Improvized Ray Tracer - CS 5721
==============================================
Compiling
* The build system used for compiling the program is cmake

To build:
* Go to the root directory
* cmake CMakeLists.txt
* make

Running the program : Executables are in the bin directory
* Use the provided shell scripts as guidelines for running the program
* The necessary help files can be accessed by using the command line switch '?'

